  "_meta": {
    "what": "Frozen public API surface of the 0.3x consumer line (bpt-agent-sdk), used by tests/legacy-consumer-0-3x.test.ts to prove 0.52+ stays drop-in for a 0.3x-pinned consumer.",
    "how": "Enumerated with the TypeScript compiler API (checker.getExportsOfModule on src/index.ts; Options via getDeclaredTypeOfSymbol().getProperties()) against the historical trees below. Regenerate by checking out the commits and re-running the same enumeration.",
