        "date": "2026-07-10",
        "path": "projects/bpt-agent-sdk"
      },
      "0.37.1": {
        "commit": "cbdbfa184",
        "date": "2026-07-10",
        "path": "projects/bpt-agent-sdk",
        "note": "the ACTUAL black-pool BPT pin (keeper, 2026-07-12). Twin-build caveat: the 0.38.0 feature build (f76f57c83, custom slash commands) also self-reports 0.37.1 (version-constant mishap repaired in 0.39.0); both builds were enumerated and their export surfaces are IDENTICAL, so this single entry covers either tarball. The difference is behavioral only (slash-command expansion) — disambiguate on-box via dist/engine/slash-commands.js presence."
      }
    },
